Item ID2862

Achey logs are logs only available to members. They can be obtained at level 1 Woodcutting from Achey trees for 25 experience each. Players can burn these logs at level 1 Firemaking for 40 experience each.

These logs are needed for the Big Chompy Bird Hunting quest to make ogre arrows, as well as composite ogre bows for Zogre Flesh Eaters.

With a knife they can be made into a random amount of 2-6 ogre arrow shafts for 1.5 Fletching experience per shaft made. With a knife and wolf bones, players can make an unstrung comp bow.

After giving Uglug Nar a relicym's balm during Zogre Flesh Eaters, he will open his store which stocks 100 achey tree logs at a base price of 4 coins. Uglug's store is the best way to obtain Achey logs.
